i> <span>Facebook</span> </a> </li> <li class="share-twitter"> <a href="http://twitter.com/intent/tweet?url=http%3A%2F%2Fexpresso.sapo.pt%2Fopiniao%2F2018-05-11-Porque-uma-Estrategia-de-Seguranca-Nacional-&amp;text=Porqu%C3%AA%20uma%20Estrat%C3%A9gia%20de%20Seguran%C3%A7a%20Nacional%3F&amp;via=expresso" data-type="twitter" class="shareToolsEntry js-share gs-foreign-tracking gs-provider-twitter" target="_blank" title="Twitter"> <i class="icon icon-twitter"></i> <span>Twitter</span> </a> </li> <li class="share-mail"> <a href="mailto:?subject=Porqu%C3%AA%20uma%20Estrat%C3%A9gia%20de%20Seguran%C3%A7a%20Nacional%3F&amp;body=Porqu%C3%AA%20uma%20Estrat%C3%A9gia%20de%20Seguran%C3%A7a%20Nacional%3F%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0A%0D%0ALer mais: http%3A%2F%2Fexpresso.sapo.pt%2Fopiniao%2F2018-05-11-Porque-uma-Estrategia-de-Seguranca-Nacional-" data-type="email" title="Email" class="shareToolsEntry gs-foreign-tracking gs-provider-email"> <i class="icon icon-mail"></i> <span>Email</span> </a> </li> <li class="share-whatsapp"> <a href="whatsapp://send?text=Porqu%C3%AA%20uma%20Estrat%C3%A9gia%20de%20Seguran%C3%A7a%20Nacional%3F%20http%3A%2F%2Fexpresso.sapo.pt%2Fopiniao%2F2018-05-11-Porque-uma-Estrategia-de-Seguranca-Nacional-" class="shareToolsEntry" data-type="whatsapp" target="_blank" title="Whatsapp" style="display:none"> <i class="icon icon-whatsapp"></i> <span>Whatsapp</span> </a> </li> <li class="share-showMore"> <div class="shareToolsEntry"> <i class="icon icon-dot-3"></i> <span>Mais</span> </div> <div class="moreShareTools"> <div class="moreShareToolsInner"> <ul> <li class="share-google+"> <a href="http://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fexpresso.sapo.pt%2Fopiniao%2F2018-05-11-Porque-uma-Estrategia-de-Seguranca-Nacional-" data-type="googleplus" class="shareToolsEntry js-share gs-foreign-tracking gs-provider-google" target="_blank" title="Google+"> <i class="icon icon-gplus"></i> <span>Google+</span> </a> </li> <li class="share-linkedin"> <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArti